{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0afb3dfcdc","title":"向“四.八”被难烈士致哀","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3713f61fde","index":0,"year":1946,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui2","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1943-1949卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui2a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9ba0a5c685","type":"title","text":"向“四.八”被难烈士致哀","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3520597bf6","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的战友们，不朽的英雄们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"473c42b707","type":"paragraph","text":"数十年间，你们为人民的事业做了轰轰烈烈的工作。今天，你们为人民事业而死，虽死犹生！","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c97ca700a","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的死是一个号召，它将加深中国人民对中国共产党的认识，它将加强中国人民坚持和平、民主、团结事业的决心。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f342675db7","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的死是一个号召，它将号召全党党员和全国人民团结起来，为和平、民主、团结的新中国而奋斗到底。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6051dd4afd","type":"paragraph","text":"全党党员和全国人民，将继承你们的遗志，继续奋斗，直到胜利，决不懈怠，决不退缩！","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34d89473d4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f82344577b","type":"subdate","text":"（一九四六年四月二十日《解放日报》）","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"0afb3dfcdc","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":169,"end":168}}}},"__N_SSG":true}